title: Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince
description: As Voldemort’s power grows, Harry Potter uncovers critical memories from the past that may hold the key to defeating him. Guided by Professor Dumbledore, Harry learns more about Voldemort’s origins while grappling with teenage romance, jealousy, and the dark secrets of the Half-Blood Prince’s potion book.

title: Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix

description: In his third year at Hogwarts, Harry learns that Sirius Black, an escaped prisoner, is after him. As he unravels the truth about his parents’ betrayal, Harry uncovers long-buried secrets and learns to wield the powerful Patronus charm to fend off the soul-sucking Dementors.

title: Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire
description: Harry unexpectedly becomes a competitor in the dangerous Triwizard Tournament. As he faces life-threatening challenges, dark forces gather, culminating in Voldemort’s return. The events mark a turning point in the wizarding world, as the shadow of war looms ever closer.
